===Noun===
'''sugilite'''

#{{mineralogy}} A [[mineral]] with [[hexagonal]] crystals, often pink or purple but can have different colors, [[potassium|K]][[sodium|Na]]<sub>2</sub>([[iron|Fe]]<sup>2+</sup>,[[manganese|Mn]]<sup>2+</sup>,[[aluminum|Al]])<sub>2</sub>[[lithium|Li]]<sub>3</sub>[[silicon|Si]]<sub>12</sub>[[oxygen|O]]<sub>30</sub>.

